lper/usage-31","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#总结回顾","content":"**获取源码并安装依赖**：从 GitHub 克隆项目，创建虚拟环境，并安装所需的 Python 库"},"567":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-32","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#总结回顾","content":"**配置购票参数**：根据目标场馆和项目，修改脚本中的参数（`courses`、`stuid`、`stuname`、`cookies`）以匹配准备预约的时间和场地"},"568":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-33","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#总结回顾","content":"**运行脚本**：执行 Python 脚本，让它自动完成购票流程"},"569":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-34","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#常见问题","content":"由于不需要处理界面，只需要向目标接口发起网络请求，因此速度更快，效率更高。但行为特征较明显，服务器更容易识别为自动化操作。\n不过这类相对不重要的校园系统通常不会特别严格地防护。"},"570":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-35","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#常见问题","content":"Cookie 的有效期通常只有 3\\~4 小时。建议在抢票前半小时内重新登录并获取最新 Cookie，以确保脚本能正常工作。"},"571":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-36","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#继续探索","content":"用 Playwright 自动打开浏览器并登录，用于获取 Cookie"},"572":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-37","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#继续探索","content":"用「任务计划程序」定时运行脚本（图形化界面 或 命令行界面）"},"573":{"id":"/docs/vhs","page_id":"/docs/vhs","type":"page","content":"VHS","tags":[],"url":"/docs/vhs"},"574":{"id":"/docs/vhs-0","page_id":"/docs/vhs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vhs","content":"VHS 是一款开源的终端录制工具。"},"575":{"id":"/docs/vhs-1","page_id":"/docs/vhs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vhs","content":"https\\://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs"},"576":{"id":"/docs/vhs/install","page_id":"/docs/vhs/install","type":"page","content":"如何安装 VHS","tags":[],"url":"/docs/vhs/install"},"577":{"id":"/docs/vhs/install-0","page_id":"/docs/vhs/insta